#use crisis.dta
gen n=_n
tsset n, monthly
library(tidyverse)
library(haven) # .dta 

df <- read_dta(file = "crisis.dta")
ts <- ts(df[,c("labor", "oil_b_rub", "rwage", "u")], start = c(1999, 1), end = c(2009, 12), frequency = 12)
reg rwage u oil_b_rub
lin_m1 <- lm(ts[,"rwage"] ~ ts[,"oil_b_rub"] + ts[,"u"])
summary(lin_m1)

## lm(formula = ts[, "rwage"] ~ ts[, "oil_b_rub"] + ts[, "u"])
